    "body": "I cannot be sure from the description itself, but it seems like you are facing a problem with winforms synchronization context.\n\nThis article should explain the deadlock:\nhttp://blog.stephencleary.com/2012/07/dont-block-on-async-code.html\n\nFrom where exactly are you calling the `server.KillAsync().Wait()` line? (it that from the UI thread? looks like it is).\n"
