    "body": "Thanks for the article and merging as #6984 . I was using the current master.\n\n`KillAnync()` was called from the console thread. I only have instantiated the form and have not even called `Application.Run`, nor have I invoked it on the form or called `Show()` on it. Just creating an instance was enough to trigger the problem. This is what made me wonder.\n\nI will continue my tests with the newest master and hope that everything works :) If not, I will write again.\n"
